title: Talking Zootopia+ with Director Josie Trinidad | What's Up, Disney+

media:group.media:title: Talking Zootopia+ with Director Josie Trinidad | What's Up, Disney+
media:group.media:description:
In honor of Filipino American History Month, host Jenny Lorenzo talks with Zootopia+ director Josie Trinidad about representation, her journey, and what audiences can expect from the new series of shorts streaming November 9 on #DisneyPlus.
